<li>Celebrate your special day with joy and the love of your family.</li>
<li>You make every day brighter; have an amazing birthday!</li>
<li>May your birthday be a reflection of the love and happiness you bring to our lives.</li>
<li>Cheers to another year of making memories with the best [Mom/Dad/Sibling/etc.].</li>
<li>Happy Birthday!  We're so lucky to have you in our family.</li>
<li>Sending you lots of love on your special day.</li>
<li>Have a fantastic birthday filled with joy and surrounded by family.</li>
    

